# Software Tests

<rule>
name: software_tests
description: On any code change, the `mise run tests` command line must be executed and pass successfully.
filters:
  - type: event
    pattern: ".*"  # Match any event
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: ".*"  # Match any file extension
actions:
  - type: execute
    command: "mise run tests"
    require_success: true
    message: "All software tests must pass before merging."
</rule>

